***You will need to use the [JAVA API Documentation](https://developers.google.com/resources/api-libraries/documentation/calendar/v3/java/latest/) for Google Calendar***

You have to create a new Meet request and then append it to the current event and before that, enable the conferenceDataVersion by setting it to 1. Before using the following code make sure that you have this [setup](https://developers.google.com/calendar/quickstart/java?authuser=1#step_3_set_up_the_sample).


